H3-2: 同季節 Brier 悪化 Welch + paired t-test + bootstrap CI
======================================================================

Input data (v4 §1.1 N1 月次 Brier 表 由来、p_win Brier):

  2025:
    2025-01: brier=0.0996 (n=240)
    2025-02: brier=0.0922 (n=300)
    2025-03: brier=0.0914 (n=336)
    2025-04: brier=0.0712 (n=264)
    2025-05: brier=0.0906 (n=312)
  2026:
    2026-01: brier=0.0601 (n=276)
    2026-02: brier=0.0791 (n=324)
    2026-03: brier=0.0807 (n=300)
    2026-04: brier=0.1167 (n=264)
    2026-05: brier=0.1250 (n=144)

----------------------------------------------------------------------
Test: Jan-May 5 pairs
----------------------------------------------------------------------
  n_2025=5, n_2026=5
  mean_2025=0.0890, std_2025=0.0106
  mean_2026=0.0923, std_2026=0.0274
  delta = mean(2026) - mean(2025) = +0.0033

  Welch (unpaired, equal_var=False): t=+0.252, p_two_sided=0.8104, p_one_sided_greater=0.4052
  Paired (ttest_rel):                t=+0.209, p_two_sided=0.8446, p_one_sided_greater=0.4223

  Welch power (two-sided alpha=0.05, target_power=0.80):
    observed_power=0.0550 (effect_delta=+0.0033, SE=0.0131, df=5.164, ncp=+0.252)
    delta needed for 80% power at same n/std = +0.0458

  Bootstrap CI (n_resample=10000, ci=0.95):
    observed delta = +0.0033
    bootstrap median = +0.0033, 95% CI = [-0.0192, +0.0266]
    P(delta > 0 | bootstrap) = 0.6039

----------------------------------------------------------------------
Test: Apr-May 2 pairs (subset)
----------------------------------------------------------------------
  n_2025=2, n_2026=2
  mean_2025=0.0809, std_2025=0.0137
  mean_2026=0.1208, std_2026=0.0059
  delta = mean(2026) - mean(2025) = +0.0399

  Welch (unpaired, equal_var=False): t=+3.787, p_two_sided=0.1118, p_one_sided_greater=0.0559
  Paired (ttest_rel):                t=+7.198, p_two_sided=0.0879, p_one_sided_greater=0.0439

  Welch power (two-sided alpha=0.05, target_power=0.80):
    observed_power=0.3405 (effect_delta=+0.0399, SE=0.0106, df=1.354, ncp=+3.787)
    delta needed for 80% power at same n/std = +0.0960

  Bootstrap CI (n_resample=10000, ci=0.95):
    observed delta = +0.0399
    bootstrap median = +0.0399, 95% CI = [+0.0261, +0.0538]
    P(delta > 0 | bootstrap) = 1.0000

======================================================================
Gate-2 (a) verdict
======================================================================

primary test: Jan-May 5 pairs (= handoff §「事前予想」が想定)

  Welch p_two_sided = 0.8104 → 弱く支持 (p>=0.20) = Gate-2 (a) FAIL
  Power = 0.0550 (effect_delta=+0.0033, n=5 vs 5, target_power_delta=+0.0458)
  Invariant 1 verdict: power < 0.80 のため、Gate-2 (a) FAIL は 「bias なし」ではなく「判定保留 / replication test 必須」と解釈する。

  Paired p_two_sided = 0.8446 → 弱く支持 (p>=0.20) = Gate-2 (a) FAIL (補助)

secondary test: Apr-May 2 pairs (= v4 §1.1 +3.3σ 観察の正面検定)

  Welch p_two_sided = 0.1118 → border zone (0.10<=p<0.20) = Gate-2 (a) FAIL (n=2 vs 2 で power 極小、参考値)
  Power = 0.3405 (effect_delta=+0.0399, n=2 vs 2, target_power_delta=+0.0960)

----------------------------------------------------------------------
総合判定:
----------------------------------------------------------------------

  primary (Jan-May Welch p=0.8104) を **公式 Gate-2 (a) 判定** とする。
  bootstrap CI の P(delta > 0) と paired test の方向で補強。

  Welch 採択理由: handoff §「事前予想」が ttest_ind を指定。
  paired を補助で見る理由: 同月同曜日 (Jan-Jan, Feb-Feb, ...) は
    競馬週ごとの schedule 差で paired より independent に近い。
    両 test の verdict が一致するかが robustness の検証になる。

